 * so we must check them additionally
 *   EQUALS (0x3D)
 *   HYPHEN (0x2D)
 *   UNDERSCORE (0x5F)
 *   DIGIT (0x30-0x39)
 *   ALPHA (0x41-0x5A and 0x61-0x7A)
